entry.name: _REENT_CHECK(var,what,type,size,init)
entry.value: do { struct _reent *_r = (var); if (_r->what == NULL) { _r->what = (type)malloc(size); __reent_assert(_r->what); init; } } while (0)

entry.name: __LOCK_INIT(class,lock)
entry.value: extern struct __lock __lock_ ## lock; class _LOCK_T lock = &__lock_ ## lock
